    <string name="settings_automated_tracking">Ukulandelela okuzenzakalelayo</string>
    <string name="settings_automated_tracking_text"><![CDATA[
Ukulandelela okuzenzakalelayo kungenzeka ngokuxhumanisa nezinhlelo zokusebenza zangaphandle ezikwazi ukwenza imisebenzi ngokuzenzakalelayo uma kwenzeka izenzakalo ezithile. Lezi zinhlelo zingathumela umlayezo kuhlelo lokusebenza ukuze luqale noma luyeke isibali sikhathi somsebenzi.<br/>
<br/>
Izibonelo zezehlakalo:<br/>
- Ukuqalisa uhlelo oluthile.<br/>
- Ukuhlola ilebula ye-NFC.<br/>
- Ukuya endaweni ethile.<br/>
- Izikhathi ezithile zosuku.<br/>
- Ukuxhuma kwiBluetooth noma iWifi.<br/>
<br/>
Ukuvumela le ndlela, izinhlelo zokusebenza kufanele zikwazi ukuthumela \"intent\" noma \"broadcast intent\" enale midlalo:<br/>
<br/>
<b>Isenzo</b> - \"%s\" or \"%s\".<br/>
<b>Okungeziwe</b> - \"%s\" negama lomsebenzi okufanele uqale noma uyeke.<br/>
<b>Iphakeji</b> - \"%s\".<br/>
    ]]></string>
    <string name="settings_automated_tracking_send_events">Thumela izehlakalo</string>
    <string name="settings_automated_tracking_send_events_text"><![CDATA[
Uma isethingi <b>\"%s\"</b> ivuliwe, uhlelo luzothumela izehlakalo uma umsebenzi uqale noma uyeke ukuze lusetshenziswe ukuzenzakalelayo kwezinye izinhlelo.<br/>
    ]]></string>
